              "avatar": [
                {
                  "width": 64,
                  "height": 64,
                  "url": "https://44.media.tumblr.com/a/a/a/a.gif",
                  "accessories": []
                }
              ],
              "tumblrmart_accessories": {},
              "can_show_badges": true,
              "active": true,
              "show_follow_action": true
            }
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "2. Create a config file in your .config folder.",
                "subtype": "heading1"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "The location of the .config folder can vary based on operating system. But it is usually located in the following location."
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "{user home}/.config",
                "subtype": "quote"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Example: C:\\Users\\tumblralina\\.config",
                "subtype": "quote"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Within that folder, create a file called 'tumblr-dt.json'."
              }
            ],
            "layout": [],
            "post": {
              "id": "111111111111111111"
            },
            "blog": {
              "name": "tutorial-fairy",
              "title": "Tutorial fairy",
              "description": "Hi! I teach people how to set up this program!",
              "url": "tutorial land",
              "uuid": "t:",
              "updated": 1772222222,
              "subscribed": false,
              "can_subscribe": false,
              "followed": false,
              "avatar": [
                {
                  "width": 64,
                  "height": 64,
                  "url": "https://44.media.tumblr.com/a/a/a/a.gif",
                  "accessories": []
                }
              ],
              "tumblrmart_accessories": {},
              "can_show_badges": true,
              "active": true,
              "show_follow_action": true
            }
          },
          {
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "3. Fill the config file.",
                "subtype": "heading1"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Open up the 'tumblr-dt.json' with any text editor, then paste the contents of this URL.\n https://github.com/Marmcie/tumblr-dashboard-terminal/blob/main/tumblr-dt.json.example"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Then replace the consumer_key and secret_key value with the ones you received on step 1. and update the redirect_port to the port you registered earlier. (If you just copied the example, value here should be '6969'!)"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Once done, hit the save, then relaunch the application."
              }
            ],
